                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="50"><div class="service-card"><div class="ico"><i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i></div><h5>Custom Apps on Creator</h5><p>Distributor management, field sales, service desks, asset management — fully integrated.</p></div></div>
