                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="50"><div class="service-card"><div class="ico"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-pie"></i></div><h5>Analytics &amp; AI (Zia)</h5><p>Executive dashboards, KPIs, anomaly detection and AI-assisted automation across Zoho apps.</p></div></div>
